### Get Metrics Summary
# Get aggregated metrics summary for a user with specific metric type and period
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}/metrics/summary?metric_type=heart_rate&period=week
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Metrics Data
# Get raw metric data for a user filtered by metric type
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}/metrics/data?metric_type=heart_rate
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

